SmartWithBadEq.agda:12.1-16.18: warning: -W[no]RewriteLHSNotNeutral
_ : true ≡ w  is not a legal rewrite rule, since the left-hand side
of a rewrite rule introduced by with/rewrite is not neutral
when checking that the clause
f with true
f | true = ?
f | false = ?
  where
    mutual
      syntax eq ...
      postulate eq : true ≡ false
      eq = refl
has type Nat

